---
description: Container startup sequence contract
globs:
  - docker/**
  - app/main.py
alwaysApply: true
---

# Docker/runtime guardrails

- Container startup must run this order: prepare vault path -> instantiate vault -> validate contract -> sync/build site -> start FastAPI.
- Serve API and published site from the same container/process boundary.
- Keep secrets out of image layers; use env vars/runtime mounts.
- Support SSH-based vault access through agent forwarding or runtime credentials.
- Do not auto-push vault git changes from startup or ingest flows.
